	abstract = {Recently, the scaling properties of the Mars topography have been 
analysed through the Wavelet Leaders Method (WLM) [1]. The scalings of
some signals (15 \%) departs significantly from the others. They can be
explained by the presence of specifics regions such as craters. These
scalings can disrupt the fractal study of the signals and the
