using the S{\textasciicircum}ν spaces\vphantom{\{}\}, Communications in Nonlinear Science and
Numerical Simulation, 56, 526-543, 2018.
\{doi.org/10.1016/j.cnsns.2017.08.029\}},
	urldate = {2021-02-25},
